DISCLAIMER: This project is provided strictly for educational and research
purposes. It documents reverse engineering techniques applied to a locally
installed application binary. No copyrighted source code, binaries, or
proprietary assets from the target application are included in this repository.
The techniques described are intended to advance understanding of Electron
application internals, native Node.js addon security, and binary analysis.
Use of these techniques against software you do not own or have authorization
to modify may violate the application's Terms of Service and/or applicable law.
The authors accept no responsibility for misuse.
